name: Silhouette Sunset - Tinder Project x Yves Saint Laurent
description: TP(XO1) - One of a kind Tinder Project x Yves Saint Laurent vintage jacket. Exclusively had-designed at our studios using Tibetan Fargesia bamboo. Coral and cobalt blend to create an Oriental dusk scene. Model is 6ft 4", and this piece can be worn either as a large or extra-large. As the original jacket is an item of genuine vintage clothing from Yves Saint Laurent, there are minor signs of wear which easily go unnoticed. Inspired by then, made for now.

name: Tinder Project Premium Red Blue Hatch Pocket Crop Top
description: (TP556) Limited run Tinder Project crop top. White short-shirt, 100% cotton and naturally inspired! Pocket is of red and blue design and also is 100% cotton. A Tinder Project wooden button has also been carefully stitched onto the top. On the sleeve a Tinder Project docket tag has also been stitched, adding a unique flair. Model is 5ft6" and wears a small, equivalent to a UK 8/10. These are all unique and handmade, so yours may differ slightly from the photographed crop top. Sleeves are also stitched rolled up, perfect for festival wear!

name: Handmade Mother Of Pearl & Shell Button Studs
description: The earrings are handmade button studs, which are 11mm in diameter, and are backed with silver plated posts and butterfly backs. Plenty of care and attention goes into fashioning each individual one to ensure quality and consistency. They come in both styles, either iridescent mother of pearl effect or a rustic shell effect. The buttons themselves are made of acrylic and are bonded to the backing using a hypo-allergenic jewellery adhesive. Perfect for summer and all skin tones!
